s":[740,3724,9671,1913537,3149391],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2023，疫情后的这一年，不易。 这是一条原计划几天前发出的视频。没想到，18日夜里突然地震。生命中总有意外和困境，怎么度过去？ 这一年，我们「相对论」采访了很多普通人—— 比如小伟，我今年第一个采访的人。他带着爸妈，在北京开小馆，是很多北漂湖北人心中「家的味道」。本以为，熬过疫情就算熬过冬天，汪爹爹却意外离世。 年终再见，小馆已从独立的店面，搬到了地下的档口。店面变小了，汪婆婆还在做她的小卤菜，小伟也在研制新菜品，「一口到武汉，特别好吃」。母子俩仍然在很艰难地从悲伤里往外走，想各种办法改善经营，计划着来年，新开一个更好的店铺。 武汉人的心气——「只要不下桌，就有机会」。 这一年，你有没有经历「不一定能看到结果的坚持」？那是一种怎样的体验？"},"attached_info":"CkAIvuL3p6CgxNZbEAMaCTEwMjk4NjMyNCCFhrWrBjAAON0BQBZyCTYzMzE4NTIxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"60 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1703654072.102258","card_id":"Q_635928249","target":{"id":635928249,"title":"作为跑步爱好者，哪个身体部位受伤会让你最担心？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/635928249","type":"question","created":1703139030,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":29,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[844,5897,106007,108296],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvuL3p6CgxNZbEAMaCTEwMzU5NTc2NSDWrY+sBjAAOB1AF3IJNjM1OTI4MjQ5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c83c672e0cb7243674ac0f0330fba564_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1703654072.102650","card_id":"Q_636105157","target":{"id":636105157,"title":"2023 年在旅行领域创作是一种怎样的体验？你有哪些成长和收获？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/636105157","type":"question","created":1703224800,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":40,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[444,482,1575,24346,32352],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvuL3p6CgxNZbEAMaC